{"lastModified":1759350080577,"uri":"c::21836669044::vessel::d5cc7852-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area:\nSummer: Bahamas, USA - New England, USA - Florida East Coast, USA - North East\nWinter: Caribbean Virgin Islands (US/BVI), Bahamas, Caribbean Leewards, Caribbean Windwards, Canary Islands\n\nChartering the 94 Lazzara Tranquility offers an unparalleled luxury yachting experience, appealing to those seeking the ultimate in comfort, style, and adventure on the water. Here’s why people would be drawn to chartering this magnificent yacht:\nLuxurious Accommodation: The 94 Lazzara Tranquility is designed with opulence in mind. It features spacious cabins, each meticulously appointed with high-end furnishings, deluxe bedding, and state-of-the-art entertainment systems. Whether for a family vacation, corporate retreat, or any type of party or celebration, the yacht offers ample space and privacy for all guests.\nExceptional Amenities: From sun-drenched decks equipped with loungers and a Jacuzzi on the flybridge, to elegant dining areas and fully stocked bars, every detail aboard the Tranquility exudes luxury. Guests can indulge in gourmet meals prepared by skilled chefs or having their food catered and brought on board to be served by the crew.\nCustomized Itineraries: Chartering the 94 Lazzara Tranquility allows for flexibility in planning. Guests can tailor their journey to explore exclusive destinations, secluded beaches, and vibrant coastal towns, all while enjoying personalized service from a professional crew dedicated to meeting every need.\nWater Sports and Recreation: The yacht is equipped with a range of water sports equipment, such as jet skis, paddleboards, and snorkeling gear, enhancing the charter experience with opportunities for adventure and exploration in the crystal-clear waters of the world’s most beautiful seas.\nPrivacy and Exclusivity: Chartering a private yacht like the Tranquility provides a level of privacy and exclusivity that cannot be matched by traditional vacation options. Guests can escape the crowds and enjoy intimate gatherings with loved ones or important business meetings in a serene and picturesque setting.\nUnforgettable Experiences: Whether cruising along the keys, exploring the Bahamas, or discovering the hidden gems of Miami or New York, the Tranquility offers unforgettable experiences and breathtaking vistas that redefine luxury travel on the water.\nIn summary, chartering the 94 Lazzara Tranquility appeals to discerning travelers looking to indulge in a luxurious, customizable, and exclusive yachting experience that promises relaxation, adventure, and memories to last a lifetime.","blueprint":{"name":"TRANQUILITY","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7852-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::659ce960-8d8e-11f0-8f6c-09ae70becac1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7852-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::659e7001-8d8e-11f0-8f6c-09ae70becac1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7852-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::65959660-8d8e-11f0-8f6c-09ae70becac1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7852-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::659632a0-8d8e-11f0-8f6c-09ae70becac1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7852-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::659e7000-8d8e-11f0-8f6c-09ae70becac1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7852-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::65906640-8d8e-11f0-8f6c-09ae70becac1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7852-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::6596a7d0-8d8e-11f0-8f6c-09ae70becac1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7852-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::659e21e0-8d8e-11f0-8f6c-09ae70becac1/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cc7852-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::65960b90-8d8e-11f0-8f6c-09ae70becac1/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Lazzara","model":"","maxCrew":4,"sleeps":8,"ba